    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for practical transportation. While the engine and transmission are solid due to consistent maintenance, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side, and some fading of the clear coat on the roof. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats. It\u2019s a dependable car that has plenty of life left, provided you don't mind the cosmetic blemishes.",
