      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning driver to acquire a machine of uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity.",
