    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a true 'time capsule' specimen in flawless condition. The exterior finish is impeccable, retaining its deep factory brilliance with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it has been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed under my care. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, featuring pristine leather upholstery with no bolster wear and a dashboard that remains free of any UV exposure or aging. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a complete, documented service history performed strictly by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and clean, reflecting a life of meticulous maintenance and fair-weather driving only. For the buyer seeking a showroom-quality vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
